comments.body:
This is the equivalent of (in C):

```
char *s = malloc(8);
memcpy(s, "testing", 8);
free(s);
fopen(s, "a");
```

Try this:

```
std::string file = GetDebugLogName();
fileout = fopen(file.c_str(), "a");
```
